div.h1: Montgomery, the gateway to the European Quarter!

div.p: Montgomery, Cinquantenaire, Schuman and Mérode. A great quality of life within a stone's throw of the business quarter.

div.h1: Is Brussels still a buyer's market?

div.p: The Brussels property market is still full of opportunities. View our tips for a successful purchase.

div.h1: Experience the good life in Rhode-Saint-Genèse

div.p: This green, residential and tranquil area offers a range of prestigious villas and beautiful houses.

div.h1: Make your garden an integral part of your home

div.p: Over the past few years, garden landscaping has become all the rage and homeowners are spending more on their outdoor space.
